18#include <string>
19#include "BitMatrix.h"
20
21namespace ZXing {
22namespace Aztec {
23
24/**
25* Aztec 2D code representation
26*
27* @author Rustam Abdullaev
28*/
29struct EncodeResult
30{
31 bool compact;
32 int size;
33 int layers;
34 int codeWords;
35 BitMatrix matrix;
36};
37
38/**
39* Generates Aztec 2D barcodes.
40*
41* @author Rustam Abdullaev
42*/
43class Encoder
44{
45public:
46 static const int DEFAULT_EC_PERCENT = 33; // default minimal percentage of error check words
47 static const int DEFAULT_AZTEC_LAYERS = 0;
48
49 static EncodeResult Encode(const std::string& data, int minECCPercent, int userSpecifiedLayers);
50};
51
52} // Aztec
53} // ZXing
